name: cred-rea-fish-team-belt-transect-survey-at-laysan-2004
notes: Belt transects along 3 consecutively-placed, 25m transect lines were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 3 sites at Laysan in the Northwest Hawaiian Islands in September 2004 from the NOAA vessel Hi'ialakai (HI04-01). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
